Title: VARIOUS: KENNETH BRANAGH AND EMMA THOMPSON SEPARATE AFTER SIX YEARS OF MARRIAGE

Summary: CANNES, FRANCE/ UNKNOWN LOCATION, AFRICA AND LONDON, ENGLAND, UNITED KINGDOM (SEPTEMBER 30 - OCTOBER 1, 1995, RECENT AND FILE) (RTV, GMTV, POLYGRAM - PART NO ACCESS UK AND PART MUST COURTESY POLYGRAM) LONDON, ENGLAND, UNITED KINGDOM (SEPTEMBER 30, 1995) (GMTV - NO ACCESS UK) 1. LV/SV NEWSPAPERS COMING OFF PRESS (2 SHOTS) 0.08 2. SV NEWSPAPER BEING TAKEN OUT OF PRESS RUN / FRONT PAGE SHOWING STORY OF SEPARATION OF BRITISH ACTORS KENNETH BRANAGH, 34, AND EMMA THOMPSON, 35 0.17 CANNES, FRANCE (RECENT - SEPTEMBER 1993)(RTV - ACCESS ALL) 3. GV/SV BRANAGH AND THOMPSON ARRVING FOR A PREMIERE (2 SHOTS) 0.24 LONDON, ENGLAND, UNITED KINGDOM (RECENT)(RTV - ACCESS ALL) 4. SV THOMPSON AT NEWS CONFERENCE ON HER LATEST MOVIE CARRINGTON. 0.31 UNIDENTIFIED LOCATION 5. CU ADVERTISEMENT FOR BRANAGH'S FILM 'FRANKENSTEIN' 0.34 6. SV BRANAGH AT PREMIERE 0.44 (MUST COURTESY POLYGRAM) 7. CLIP FROM FILM "CARRINGTON" WITH THOMPSON 0.58 LONDON, ENGLAND, UNITED KINGDOM (GMTV - NO ACCESS UK) 8. SCU THOMPSON SPEAKING ABOUT THE CHARACTER OF CARRINGTON (ENGLISH) 1.19 UNKNOWN LOCATION, AFRICA (FILE)(RTV - ACCESS ALL) 9. SCU/SV BRANAGH (2 SHOTS) 1.27 10.SCU BRANAGH SPEAKING ABOUT HIS ROLE AS A DIRECTOR (ENGLISH) 1.42 LONDON, ENGLAND, UNITED KINGDOM (OCTOBER 1, 1995) (GMTV - NO ACCESS UK) 11.SV/SLV NIGHT EXTERIORS OF THOMPSON'S HOUSE (4 SHOTS) 2.11 LONDON, ENGLAND, UNITED KINGDOM (FILE - MARCH 1995) (RTV - ACCESS ALL) 12.SV THOMPSON AND BRANAGH ARRVING AT FILM PREMIERE 2.29 SEQUENCE 8 TRANSCRIPT: THOMPSON: "I THINK THAT A PRURIENT QUESTION, TO BE HONEST, SO I'LL AVOID IT BY SAYING THAT I THINK THAT PEOPLE SHOULD EXPERIMENT WITH THE FORM, THAT THESE PEOPLE WERE EXPERIMENTING WITH THE FORM. AND THAT CARRINGTON AS A WOMAN SORT OF REFUSED TO KNUCKLE UNDER." Initials Script is copyright Reuters Limited. All rights reserved.
